- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is relevant as the paper considers systems that collect data about user activities.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses processing event streams and optimizing filter mechanisms.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper considers differential privacy guarantees for multi-input multi-output systems.
